text: Warren County is a county in the U.S. state of New Jersey. As of the 2020 Census, the county's population was 109,632. Its county seat is Belvidere.New Jersey County Map , New Jersey Department of State. Accessed July 10, 2017. It is part of the Allentown-Bethlehem-Easton, PA-NJ metropolitan statistical area in the Lehigh Valley. == References == Category:19th-century establishments in New Jersey Category:1824 establishments in the United States Category:New Jersey counties
